            <p>1 January</p>
            <p>1 May</p>
            <p>25 December</p>
            <h2>REDUCED HOURS</h2>
            <p>6 January</p>
            <p>24 and 31 December</p>
            <p>From 10.00 a.m. to 2.00 p.m.</p>
            <h2>FREE HOURS</h2>
            <p>From Monday to Saturday from 18.00 to 20.00 h.</p>
            <p>Sundays and public holidays from 5 p.m. to 7 p.m.</p>
